The reflectance, transmittance, and absorbance of the films coated on glass were measured in the wavelength range 300 nm to 900 nm. The CZTS film has a broad absorption band with absorption coefficient lying in the 104 cm−1 range. CZTS is a direct band gap material and for allowed transitions, αhν=A(hν-Eg),\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
